Package: phondist
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Phonological Distances and Neighbourhoods in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ryan Ka Yau Lai (kayaulai@connect.hku.hk)
Maintainer: Ryan Ka Yau Lai (kayaulai@connect.hku.hk)
Description: This package implements several phonological distances suggested in the literature. At the moment, only Levenshtein distance-based measures are available. Others will be added as the package progresses.
